import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Canary Dental"
	description="Learn about Canary Dental's mission, our team, and our commitment to providing premium dental care in Surrey, BC."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-04-29')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>Your Trusted Surrey Dental Clinic</h2>
	<p>
		Welcome to <strong>Canary Dental</strong>, where we combine state-of-the-art dental technology with compassionate, patient-first care. Our clinic in Surrey, BC is designed to be a welcoming environment for families, professionals, and newcomers alike. We believe that a trip to the dentist should be stress-free, transparent, and completely tailored to your needs.
	</p>

	<h2>Our Mission</h2>
	<p>
		Our mission is simple: to provide high-quality, preventative dentistry that helps our patients keep their natural smiles for a lifetime. Whether you are coming in for a routine <a href="/dental-cleaning">dental cleaning</a> or looking for advanced <a href="/dental-implants">dental implants</a>, our team is dedicated to delivering results you can be proud of.
	</p>

	<h2>Multilingual Care (English & Mandarin)</h2>
	<p>
		We understand that discussing your health and finances is much easier in your native language. That is why we are proud to offer <a href="/mandarin-speaking-dentist">comprehensive dental services in both English and Mandarin</a>. We want every patient to fully understand their treatment options without any language barriers getting in the way.
	</p>

	<h2>Modern Technology & Comfort</h2>
	<p>
		Dentistry has evolved, and so have we. We utilize digital X-rays, intraoral cameras, and modern sterilization protocols to ensure your safety and comfort. If you have dental anxiety, let us know! We take the time to explain every step of the procedure, so you always feel in control.
	</p>

	<h2>Schedule Your Visit</h2>
	<p>
		Ready to experience the Canary Dental difference? We are currently accepting new patients and are proud providers for the <a href="/cdcp-dentist">Canadian Dental Care Plan (CDCP)</a>. 
	</p>
	<p>
		Contact us today via <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/4RpjC2r6Hq">LINE</a> to book your consultation!
	</p>
</Layout>
